1
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:33,760
Nervous?

2
00:01:39,799 --> 00:01:41,200
Tomorrow, we play right here.

3
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,480
This is a privilege only

4
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:45,480
pro teams usually get.

5
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:49,840
Tens of thousands cheering for you.

6
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,120
Go for it!

7
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,319
Tens of thousands of people...

8
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,760
A dream come true.

9
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,680
Just didn't expect it like this.

10
00:02:06,079 --> 00:02:06,640
Afraid of losing?

11
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:08,800
Afraid of embarrassing yourself?

12
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,360
No.

13
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:15,240
Coach.

14
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,719
Do you think

15
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,080
we can beat Nanjing?

16
00:02:23,919 --> 00:02:24,840
Competitive sports.

17
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:27,240
To other people,

18
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:28,919
winning and losing matters a lot.

19
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,960
But for us football players,

20
00:02:33,919 --> 00:02:34,960
winning and losing is like

21
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,719
eating, sleeping.

22
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,080
It's just daily life.

23
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:42,879
Remember

24
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,960
what I always tell you?

25
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:44,680
That one line.

26
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,159
All I want is the right attitude.

27
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:56,759
That's right.

28
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,840
I just want the right attitude from you.

29
00:03:03,039 --> 00:03:03,719
Tomorrow,

30
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,199
every seat in this place

31
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:05,879
will be filled.

32
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,120
Millions of viewers

33
00:03:08,159 --> 00:03:09,120
will watch you play

34
00:03:10,199 --> 00:03:11,159
on the live broadcast.

35
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:14,400
They're not coming to see you win.

36
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,800
They want to see

37
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:19,080
if ordinary people like them

38
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:21,199
can still show

39
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,280
a fighting attitude

40
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,199
when facing

41
00:03:24,319 --> 00:03:25,400
a powerful opponent.

42
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:30,759
Success is only temporary.

43
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:34,319
Failure is the norm in life.

44
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,039
But failure

45
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:38,960
divides people into two kinds.

46
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:40,840
The first kind

47
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,240
gets crushed forever.

48
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:45,599
The other kind,

49
00:03:47,199 --> 00:03:48,319
after every fall,

50
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,199
gets back up again

51
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,400
and keeps chasing success.

52
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,120
In this world,

53
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:57,520
there's only one

54
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,759
true form of heroism.

55
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,439
It's knowing

56
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:01,759
the truth about life,

57
00:04:04,759 --> 00:04:05,960
and still loving it anyway.

58
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:48,920
Today's homework is

59
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:50,079
to write a cheering message

60
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,600
for Changzhou FC.

61
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,720
When you all go home today,

62
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:53,839
you can watch TV

63
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,759
with your mom and dad.

64
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:56,000
Watch Changzhou FC

65
00:04:56,079 --> 00:04:57,240
play against the Nanjing Team.

66
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,319
Then write down

67
00:04:58,439 --> 00:05:00,240
what you most want to say to them.

68
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,120
Cheer them on.

69
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,199
Okay?

70
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,959
Okay!

71
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:20,759
Boss.

72
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:24,680
A bowl of noodles, please.

73
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,560
What do you feel like eating today?

74
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:27,279
Go make it yourself.

75
00:05:27,519 --> 00:05:28,560
It's all on me today.

76
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:30,279
But I don't know how to cook.

77
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,079
Tell me what you want, I'll make it.

78
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,199
Stop bugging her already.

79
00:05:34,199 --> 00:05:34,920
The match is about to start.

80
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,199
Excuse me, coming through.

81
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,639
Move aside, here we go!

82
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:45,720
Xiaoyong's mom,

83
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:48,199
I think our Changzhou FC today

84
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,319
is definitely going to win.

85
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:49,759
Yeah.

86
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,839
They're definitely going to win.

87
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:51,160
Right.

88
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:53,240
Come on, come on.

89
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:54,240
Our son's first match!

90
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,120
Hurry up and watch!

91
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:57,519
A bunch of guys chasing one ball.

92
00:05:57,519 --> 00:05:58,319
What's so interesting about that?

93
00:05:58,399 --> 00:05:59,360
How is it not interesting?

94
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,360
It's so exciting!

95
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:22,800
Look!

96
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:24,160
Daddy!

97
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,240
Cut through!

98
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:31,279
Back him up!

99
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:33,000
Move up! Push forward!

100
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:36,639
Xiaoyong!

101
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:38,360
Pass to him!

102
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,439
Everyone push up!

103
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:01,360
Yes!

104
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:05,319
Create space!

105
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,399
Run, winger!

106
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,560
Changzhou!

107
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,480
Come on!

108
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:33,959
Go!

109
00:07:38,279 --> 00:07:39,000
Go!

110
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:47,839
Take it easy, no rush.

111
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:20,920
Nice play!

112
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:22,680
Nice! Nice! Nice!

113
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:28,680
Get back on defense!

114
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:29,920
Why are you all just standing there?

115
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:34,519
It's okay.

116
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:35,440
Don't cry, Duoduo.

117
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:48,639
This is just...

118
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,960
Nice! Nice! Nice!

119
00:09:17,159 --> 00:09:17,879
It's okay.

120
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,960
It's fine, it's fine.

121
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:19,840
I'm done watching, I'm done.

122
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:20,879
What's the point.

123
00:09:22,159 --> 00:09:23,480
Your son's still out there running.

124
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:24,519
What do you mean no point?

125
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:24,960
Watch!

126
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,399
He's definitely about to score.

127
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,480
There's still time!

128
00:09:41,279 --> 00:09:42,080
Hurry, play the ball!

129
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:48,960
Still time, still time!

130
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:49,879
One more shot!

131
00:09:50,519 --> 00:09:51,399
Try to score one!

132
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:52,480
Go!

133
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:57,679
Changzhou!

134
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,399
Come on!

135
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,320
Come on, Changzhou!

136
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:03,399
Come on, Changzhou!

137
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,720
Let's score one!

138
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:07,799
One goal, and we've won!

139
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,120
It's okay, it's okay.

140
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:46,320
Daddy! Daddy!

141
00:10:46,559 --> 00:10:47,639
Come on!

142
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:50,639
Come on!

143
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,639
Changzhou!

144
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,720
The outcome of the match seems decided,

145
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,879
but for Changzhou FC,

146
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:59,120
their fight is not over yet.

147
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:01,399
Though any suspense over the result

148
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:03,000
has all but disappeared,

149
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,919
everyone still wants to see

150
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:07,840
whether Changzhou FC can score a goal.

151
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:08,759
Come on!

152
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,240
Changzhou FC!

153
00:11:11,399 --> 00:11:12,519
Changzhou FC!

154
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,519
Come on!

155
00:11:16,639 --> 00:11:17,480
Changzhou!

156
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,360
Come on!

157
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,399
Come on!

158
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,480
Come on!

159
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,399
Come on!

160
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,320
Come on!

161
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,200
Come on!

162
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:25,159
Come on!

163
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:27,039
Come on, come on!

164
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,000
Come on!

165
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:28,879
Come on!

166
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:29,879
Come on!

167
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,600
He scored!

168
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,159
It's in, right?

169
00:11:53,519 --> 00:11:54,279
Goal! It's in!

170
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:56,320
Yes! We scored! Finally!

171
00:11:59,039 --> 00:11:59,480
Wait...

172
00:11:59,639 --> 00:12:00,879
The ref's calling offside.

173
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,159
Goal disallowed.

174
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,320
Oh my God.

175
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:06,039
Offside. Goal disallowed.

176
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,000
Was that really offside?

177
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:09,759
No way.

178
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:10,440
That was a great goal.

179
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,000
Right?

180
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:13,039
How could that be offside?

181
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,279
Why doesn't it count?

182
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:23,679
Head referee Cui Yueqiang

183
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:25,360
has blown the whistle

184
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,559
to end the match.

185
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:30,440
In the end, this match

186
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:32,080
sees Changzhou FC lose at home.

187
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,159
In the second half,

188
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,039
on at least four occasions,

189
00:12:39,159 --> 00:12:40,639
Changzhou FC came

190
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,639
very close to scoring,

191
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,879
incredibly close.

192
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:46,720
But

193
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:50,360
luck just wasn't on their side.

194
00:12:54,919 --> 00:12:56,399
Every ounce of all-out effort

195
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:59,320
was written on the faces

196
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,759
of Changzhou FC's players,

197
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:04,759
and in the passion of Changzhou fans

198
00:13:05,039 --> 00:13:07,559
cheering at the stadium.

199
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,639
Go, Changzhou FC!

200
00:13:12,919 --> 00:13:14,399
Congrats to the Nanjing Team.

201
00:13:45,879 --> 00:13:46,919
You gave it your all,

202
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,559
but didn't get the result you wanted.

203
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,000
That's life.

204
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,080
But today's match,

205
00:13:58,919 --> 00:14:00,200
I'm proud of you all.

206
00:14:02,519 --> 00:14:02,960
Donglin,

207
00:14:03,759 --> 00:14:05,080
you played more decisively than ever.

208
00:14:06,039 --> 00:14:06,480
Old Xie,

209
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,720
you were strong in the tackles.

210
00:14:09,679 --> 00:14:10,240
Zhou Hang,

211
00:14:10,679 --> 00:14:11,519
everyone

212
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,960
was cheering for your

213
00:14:13,039 --> 00:14:14,200
tireless running.

214
00:14:15,679 --> 00:14:16,200
Xiaoyong,

215
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:18,720
that shot was brilliant.

216
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:20,960
You just had

217
00:14:21,039 --> 00:14:21,919
a bit of bad luck.

218
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,679
And every one of you on the pitch

219
00:14:25,159 --> 00:14:26,679
showed your strengths.

220
00:14:28,039 --> 00:14:28,919
Today's match

221
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:29,840
is over.

222
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,480
But two-thirds of our season

223
00:14:31,799 --> 00:14:32,720
still lies ahead.

224
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,000
Our goal is clear:

225
00:14:37,639 --> 00:14:38,240
Win a match,

226
00:14:38,919 --> 00:14:39,480
earn a point,

227
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:41,320
score a goal.

228
00:14:42,279 --> 00:14:42,879
I'm confident

229
00:14:44,519 --> 00:14:45,639
you can make it happen.

230
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,080
Daddy! Daddy!

231
00:14:59,080 --> 00:14:59,720
Duoduo!

232
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,879
Daddy, you're amazing!

233
00:15:03,639 --> 00:15:04,120
Honey,

234
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:05,200
how's your leg?

235
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:05,919
Is it serious?

236
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:07,399
It's fine.

237
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,399
A few days' rest and I'll be okay.

238
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:09,840
You fought hard out there.

239
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:27,799
It's all good.

240
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:32,519
You guys were amazing.

241
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:36,799
Online,

242
00:15:36,799 --> 00:15:37,879
they're calling you Thirteen-Nil.

243
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:38,679
But in my heart,

244
00:15:38,799 --> 00:15:39,919
you're my Shisan Ye.

245
00:15:42,799 --> 00:15:44,200
Who pinches their Shisan Ye like that?

246
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:45,159
Easy, take it easy!

247
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:46,559
How's this?

248
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:47,480
Perfect.

249
00:15:49,759 --> 00:15:50,039
Here.

250
00:15:51,399 --> 00:15:52,320
Drink it while it's hot.

251
00:15:56,559 --> 00:15:57,360
Coach Changda,

252
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,399
do you want me to feed you?

253
00:15:59,639 --> 00:16:00,799
No, no, no need.

254
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:02,679
Come on, come on.

255
00:16:03,879 --> 00:16:04,519
Here, here, here.
